### 1. Midtrans Webhook (Payment Notification)
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}/v1/webhooks/midtrans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "order_id": "{{orderId}}",
  "status_code": "200",
  "transaction_status": "settlement",
  "gross_amount": "110000.00",
  "signature_key": "DUMMY_SIGNATURE_FOR_LOCAL_TESTING",
  "transaction_id": "mid-trans-tx-123"
}

### 2. Biteship Webhook (Shipping Notification)
POST {{protocol}}://{{host}}/v1/webhooks/biteship
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event": "order.status",
  "id": "bit-ship-webhook-789",
  "order_id": "BS-12345",
  "status": "delivered"
}
